data.name: XDispatchProviderInterceptor
desc: makes it possible to intercept request of XDispatch.
Can be registered as an interceptor by using interface XDispatchProviderInterception.

methods.name: getMasterDispatchProvider
desc: access to the master XDispatchProvider of this interceptor

methods.name: getSlaveDispatchProvider
desc: access to the slave XDispatchProvider of this interceptor

methods.name: setMasterDispatchProvider
desc: sets the master XDispatchProvider, which may forward calls to its XDispatchProvider.queryDispatch() to this dispatch provider.

methods.name: setSlaveDispatchProvider
desc: sets the slave XDispatchProvider to which calls to XDispatchProvider.queryDispatch() can be forwarded under control of this dispatch provider.
